name: fake-out
flavor_text: This attack hits first and makes the target flinch. It only works the first turn the user is in battle.
effect_text_extend: Inflicts regular damage.  Causes the target to flinch.  Can only be used on the user's first turn after entering the field.
effect_text_simple: Can only be used as the first move after the user enters battle.  Causes the target to flinch.
